reviews.text:
Food! Delicious, fresh! Did I say delicious. 
I had the Honey Mustard Chicken Cobb Salad. 
I ate the Whole huge salad, it was so yummy I could not stop...
Really neat concept! They have a small menu- salads and sandwiches made to order. Also, 2 huge cases of grab and go reheat options. Their menu rotates every...
Top notch and fresh! I'm upset I live in Cleveland, but I will be back soon to try everything else!
